Features:
	Weekly/biweekly blog style posts
	Forum space (SFW and NSFW)
		Automated forum moderation
			Key word monitoring
	Resource archive
	Group feed on site, so that site is a "one stop shop"
		Sort by new and popular?
	LFP/Dating area?

Security
	Facebook auth required so that activity is linked to FB group users and users can be removed from both simultaneously
	Facebook auth/user info is private, so that users can post with greater anonymity 

Design Philosophy
	Flat UI
	"Hero" style navigation
	Site in sections that separates content by type
	Sections navigable by page (over time) where appropriate
